										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">ATS systems now screen out over 80% of resumes before a human ever sees them, according to Qwyse’s 2026 AI resume builder guide. These resume optimization tools don’t just make your resume look better.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">They optimize it to clear that first filter. This guide covers the 10 best AI resume builder platforms tested in 2026, ranked by ATS performance, free tier value, and real-world usability.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">The job search toolkit has expanded significantly. Pairing this AI software with strong written applications makes a real difference. See the best AI for writing for tools that help with cover letters and professional communications.</span></p>
